 class EmotionMLFormatException
          An EmotionMLFormatException is an EmotionMLException thrown when importing or exporting EmotionML elements that do not comply with the EmotionML recommendation.
 class EmotionMLResolutionException
          An EmotionMLResolutionException is an EmotionMLException thrown when importing or exporting EmotionML emotions that refer to vocabularies that cannot be resolved.
 class EmotionMLValidationException
          An EmotionMLValidationException is an EmotionMLException thrown when importing or exporting EmotionML elements that cannot pass the validations.
